21 SECTION 2. EXTRA HELP - SHARED SERVICES. There is hereby authorized,
22 for the Department of Parks, Heritage, and Tourism for the 2025-2026 fiscal
23 year, the following maximum number of part-time or temporary employees, to be
24 known as "Extra Help", payable from funds appropriated herein for such
25 purposes: eleven (11) temporary or part-time employees, when needed, at rates
26 of pay not to exceed those provided in the Uniform Classification and
27 Compensation Act, or its successor, or this act for the appropriate
28 classification.
